The Shirakami Snow Bell association perfectly implements her narrative function as threshold existence between winter (human world) and spring (yokai realm). Her unconscious use of mitefuri and katarikake creates elegant implementation of instinctive spiritual aptitude that explains her compatibility with yokai realm despite human origin. The bell (鈴) symbolism in her associated flower creates sound-based connection framework that supports her ability to hear Katsuo's dialect markers from first encounter.

## MEGUMI
The Mountain Peony association creates botanical visualization framework that foreshadows her potential spiritual journey through connection to the kodama tree location. This implementation elegantly suggests her corrupting influence potential while simultaneously establishing redemption pathway through shared botanical symbolism with sacred transformation location.

